Variable Documentation

NSString* WNErrorServerMessageKey = @"WNErrorServerMessageKey"

A key that may be used to retrieve an optional, non-localized server-provided error message from an error in the WNErrorDomain.

This key may be made available for network requests if the Wordnik API server provides additional error message information in its response, and is primarily intended to assist in debugging.
